{"tid":885419,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"RTX 2080、2080 Ti 被爆出現藍屏、死機！NVIDIA 回應：波及不廣，正積極解決問題","createTime":"2018-11-01T10:05:57.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-01T17:28:10.000Z","uid":1886,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"04ec2e09a17a1faf4f7d981abb1640724ab376ff","tid":885419,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T10:05:57.000Z","msg":"NVIDIA 全新 RTX Turing 繪圖卡是迄今為止功能最強大的消費類 GPU，支援令人興奮的新遊戲視覺功能，如 DLSS 深度學習超級採樣和 Ray Tracing 光線跟踪，然而在推出了兩個多月之後，卻爆出新繪圖卡出現不穩定性、崩潰、甚至死機等問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，當中 RTX 2080 Ti Founder&rsquo;s Edition 公版特別嚴重<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。<br />\n<br />\n在 NVIDIA 官方討論區中，在過去幾星期不斷有用家在購買了全新 RTX 20 系列繪圖卡後，發現在使用時出現了崩潰<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 、藍屏<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 、死機<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 、無法正常運作等問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，報稱出現問題的繪圖卡包括了 RTX 2080 及 RTX 2080 Ti，但主要問題存在於 RTX 2080 Ti 為主。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://file.hkepc.net/2018/10/source/31200657171332914273.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffile.hkepc.net%2F2018%2F10%2Fsource%2F31200657171332914273.jpg&h=54eb9661&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n全文：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hkepc.com/17408/RTX_2080_Ti_被爆出現藍屏死機_NVIDIA_回應波及不廣正積極解決問題\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkepc.com%2F17408%2FRTX_2080_Ti_%E8%A2%AB%E7%88%86%E5%87%BA%E7%8F%BE%E8%97%8D%E5%B1%8F%E6%AD%BB%E6%A9%9F_NVIDIA_%E5%9B%9E%E6%87%89%E6%B3%A2%E5%8F%8A%E4%B8%8D%E5%BB%A3%E6%AD%A3%E7%A9%8D%E6%A5%B5%E8%A7%A3%E6%B1%BA%E5%95%8F%E9%A1%8C&d=vdidwSVWZSbQgG4wSmkdw1zEg0sy7MJ6GkP0ogsbSqo%3D&h=99256be0\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hkepc.com/17408/RTX_2080_Ti_被爆出現藍屏死機_NVIDIA_回應波及不廣正積極解決問題</a>"},{"pid":"beaf20d078b2c877db988bc569da3d736f25949e","tid":885419,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T10:07:07.000Z","msg":"這些問題似乎主要影響到 2080 Ti 的 Founder&rsquo;s Edition 版本，<span style=\"color: red;\">然而亦有用家表示在其他第三方品牌的繪圖卡亦出現了故障及問題，即使在重新安裝驅動程式及進行常規故障排除後亦無法解決問題，另外亦有用家表明在 RMA 更換回來的新卡同樣存在相同的問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/husky/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，</span>讓用家們大表不滿<img src=\"/assets/faces/husky/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，更有人懷疑這是繪圖卡的設計缺陷。<br />\n<br />\n就 RTX 20 系列繪圖卡出現問題，NVIDIA 官方特別作出回應<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，表示存在問題波及不廣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 、受到影響的人數暫時未有持續增加<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，他們和之前一樣，正在與個別用戶解決問題，至於價格較低的 RTX 2070 並未出現類似報告。"},{"pid":"9f001e96a707cfea865fa006f78648b4ac34d2be","tid":885419,"uid":171009,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T10:08:52.000Z","msg":"樓主加d表情幾好笑"},{"pid":"f35c6f12f88638feb1e37bf38ec3087b5ab3133b","tid":885419,"uid":81113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T10:13:54.000Z","msg":"係藍畫面，唔係藍屏，你鍾意講藍芒都得"},{"pid":"54a306f5b711ec7264f6822b67342c0a98bc1ee9","tid":885419,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f35c6f12f88638feb1e37bf38ec3087b5ab3133b","tid":885419,"uid":81113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T10:13:54.000Z","msg":"係藍畫面，唔係藍屏，你鍾意講藍芒都得"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T10:16:36.000Z","msg":"會同 hkepc 反映返字眼問題"},{"pid":"839db8af689616f660791700719149b879228162","tid":885419,"uid":85659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T12:40:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bfaa7ece7916147d6d29ccfa683ab7bff34db8ad","tid":885419,"uid":179467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T13:19:25.000Z","msg":"Nvidia應該又俾人集體入稟法院索償 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\"